data.description: Come home to this 4 BEDROOM & 2 BATH-CONTROL4 SMART HOUSE!!! You can program nearly every system or device in the home. This app saves you time and money. This home is designed w/an 2-STORY FOYER & a SPACIOUS floor plan. The great rm has a vaulted ceiling w/HARDWOOD flooring & a GAS FIREPLACE w/a decorative mantle. The kitchen has plenty of cabinet space, a breakfast bar, ample countertops, PANTRY, & an eating area w/a coffered ceiling. Relax in the luxurious master bedrm en-suite. It has a VAULTED CEILING & is large enough for king-sized furniture. The master-bath has a soaking tub, separate shower, private toilet, double sink vanity & a LARGE WALK-IN CLOSET. There are 2 add't bedrms, a full bath w/a dry and wet area, & a laundry rm all on the main level. Upstairs has a finished rm w/a closet that could be a 4th bedrm, OFFICE or BONUS rm. The covered patio & the FLAT-FENCED BACKYARD are ideal for outdoor fun. It's located near SCHOOLS, SHOPPING, MEDICAL and RECREATIONAL facilities!
